				<description>

&lt;div class=&quot;scp-image-block block-{$align}&quot; style=&quot;width:300px;&quot;&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;http://scp-wiki.wdfiles.com/local--files/scp-1863/limeliftoff.jpg&quot; style=&quot;width:300px;&quot; alt=&quot;limeliftoff.jpg&quot; class=&quot;image&quot; /&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;scp-image-caption&quot; style=&quot;width:300px;&quot;&gt;
&lt;p&gt;一杯由当地餐馆提供的1863-A&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;p&gt;by &lt;span class=&quot;printuser avatarhover&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/m-element&quot;  &gt;&lt;img class=&quot;small&quot; src=&quot;http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=2941964&amp;amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;amp;timestamp=1487494359&quot; alt=&quot;M Element&quot; style=&quot;background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=2941964)&quot; /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/m-element&quot;  &gt;M Element&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
