						 <p>二级研究员Cherry Pict，以她的谨小慎微和往往令人费解的行为举止而闻名。2009年末她成为了一名基金会雇员。其宣称自己在19██年自他父亲的前额合身蹦出。</p> <p>她参与了以下文档的编辑工作：<br /> <span style="text-decoration: underline;">基金会故事</span>：</p> <ul> <li>Ears</li> <li>Field Man</li> <li>Interference</li> <li>Locks</li> <li>Picking</li> <li>SCP-857-D</li> <li>Wednesday - 1</li> <li>Wednesday - 2</li> <li>Wednesday - 3</li> <li>Wednesday - 4</li> <li>Wednesday - 5</li> <li>Wednesday - 6</li> </ul> <p><span style="text-decoration: underline;">SCPs:</span></p> <ul> <li>SCP-900</li> </ul> <p><span style="text-decoration: underline;">Decommissions:</span></p> <p>by <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/airalin-knowledge" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=2952172&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1487494360" alt="Airalin_Knowledge" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=2952172)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/airalin-knowledge" >Airalin_Knowledge</a></span></p> 
