												<content:encoded>
					<![CDATA[
						 <p><em>当你恢复知觉的时候，你发现自己正在一片森林中奔跑。</em></p> <p><em>你不记得自己是怎么到这里来的了；你唯一知道的就是自己必须一直跑下去。你的体力几乎耗尽，肺部已经无力吸入空气，可是你绝对不能停下。</em></p> <p><em>这到底是为什么？怎么会变成这样的？</em></p> <p><em>你的思绪飘散开去……</em></p> <p>事情是从四天前开始的。</p> <p>那是平凡无奇的一天。你醒来，上班，下班，和家人共进晚餐，与你的伴侣一同就寝。</p> <p>可是那天晚上，你没有睡。</p> <p>并不是你不想睡觉。你就是怎么也无法闭上眼睛进入梦乡。时间慢慢过去，你却在床上翻来覆去，还唯恐弄醒了枕边人。</p> <p>2点……4点……</p> <p><em>快跑啊跑啊不要停</em></p> <p>直到早晨6点你都完全没合过眼。可是已经到了起床上班的时间。你穿衣，洗脸，吃早饭，走出家门。“没事的，”你心想，“我能在喝茶的时候补一觉，只要打个小盹就好……”</p> <p>可是你没有打盹，是不是？接下来的一整天你都没有休息。要做的工作太多了。</p> <p><em>不要停天啊不要让我停下</em></p> <p>那天晚上你又徒劳地躺在床上。翻来覆去，辗转反侧。闹钟那永无止境的滴答声简直让你抓狂。</p> <p>那天晚上你又没有睡觉。</p> <p>后一天晚上你还是没睡。</p> <p>然后……当然，昨天你也一点没睡，现在你想起来了。</p> <p><em>可恶可恶可恶为什么我要跑为什么</em></p> <p>你的家人已经注意到了。他们谈论着这件事，而你觉得头痛欲裂。你只希望他们能闭嘴闭嘴闭嘴安静一下。寂静是多么舒适，尽管你脑袋里响个不停的嗡嗡声会毁了这份感觉。</p> <p>昨天的情况很糟。你简直睁不开眼，可是你却睡不着，哦我多么希望能睡上哪怕是那么一小会求求你了。你的样子很憔悴，你的同事们这样说道。哦，多可怕！你上次睡觉是什么时候的事？他们问。他们所有的人都重复着同一个问题，同一个该死的问题，而你只希望能静上一会儿。这些噪音让你恼火。愤怒。你只想安静一下，为什么他们就不能放过你一会&#8212;</p> <p>你突然失去了知觉。</p> <p>而当你清醒过来时，你在森林中奔跑。</p> <p><em>跑啊跑啊跑啊跑啊跑啊跑啊跑啊跑啊跑啊</em></p> <p>你的双手感觉很温暖。</p> <p><em>跑啊跑啊跑啊跑啊跑啊跑啊跑啊跑啊跑啊</em></p> <p>你逐渐进入森林深处，树木越来越茂密了。你得小心；你知道，一旦摔倒的话，你就再也起不来了。</p> <p><em>跑啊跑啊跑啊跑啊跑啊跑啊跑啊跑啊跑啊&#8212;</em></p> <p>可是这是不可避免的事。你摔倒了。倒在丛林中松软的土地上。</p> <p><em>……</em></p> <p>森林中一片寂静。</p> <p><em>……</em></p> <p>你用残余的力气翻了个身，因为脸对着地面的姿势呼吸很困难。</p> <p><em>……</em></p> <p>过了一会儿，你听见了很轻的脚步声向你走来。</p> <p><em>……</em></p> <p>可是你什么也看不见。</p> <p><em>……</em></p> <p>脚步声停下了。然后，你的胃部传来一阵突如其来的尖锐疼痛。</p> <p>你想要尖叫。痛苦简直无法忍受。可是，你太累了。太累，太累。你甚至没有力气抬起头看看自己腹部的那道巨大的爪印，那道口子割裂了你的皮肉，暴露出你的内脏。</p> <p>在你最后一次合上双眼之前，你看见自己的一大块血肉从身上被撕下来，在空中停留片刻，然后伴随着一阵令人作呕的声音，在稀薄的空气中消失了。</p> <p>by <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/airalin-knowledge" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=2952172&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1487494360" alt="Airalin_Knowledge" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=2952172)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/airalin-knowledge" >Airalin_Knowledge</a></span></p> 
				 	]]>
				</content:encoded>							</item>
					<item>
				<guid>http://scp-wiki-cn.wikidot.com/observation-log-709</guid>
				<title>观察记录709</title>
				<link>http://scp-wiki-cn.wikidot.com/observation-log-709</link>
				<description>

&lt;p&gt;请写下你的名字，第一次观察的时间和日期，观察所用的时间。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;by &lt;span class=&quot;printuser avatarhover&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/m-element&quot;  &gt;&lt;img class=&quot;small&quot; src=&quot;http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=2941964&amp;amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;amp;timestamp=1487494360&quot; alt=&quot;M Element&quot; style=&quot;background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=2941964)&quot; /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/m-element&quot;  &gt;M Element&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
</description>
				<pubDate>Fri, 17 Feb 2017 13:02:02 +0000</pubDate>
												<content:encoded>
					<![CDATA[
						 <p>请写下你的名字，第一次观察的时间和日期，观察所用的时间。</p> <p><strong>姓名：</strong>特工Talmor<br /> <strong>日期：</strong>04/01/2009<br /> <strong>时间：</strong>约23:15<br /> <strong>时长：</strong>约20分钟<br /> <strong>所见：</strong>一窝穿着连指手套和靴子的浣熊在雪地里嬉戏。它们打雪仗，堆雪浣熊，还进行了其他冬天的娱乐活动。</p> <p><strong>姓名：</strong>特工Thompson<br /> <strong>日期：</strong>06/01/2009<br /> <strong>时间：</strong>19:30<br /> <strong>时长：</strong>23分钟<br /> <strong>所见：</strong>一些野生动物在使用现代自动武器和几把未来激光炮进行作战，包括熊，鹿，狼，鸟，羊，浣熊和松鼠（皆为双足直立行走）。</p> <p><strong>姓名：</strong>Dr. █████<br /> <strong>日期：</strong>01/08/████<br /> <strong>时间：</strong>12:00<br /> <strong>时长：</strong>30分钟<br /> <strong>所见：</strong></p> <ol> <li>在观察中一直使用四只脚移动的巨大树状生物。有时看起来在摇“树枝”，和[数据删除]。</li> <li>一只巨大的蛇状蜥蜴，拥有似乎是胸腔一部分的滑翔翼。</li> <li>一小窝灰熊，有类似变色龙的舌头，在胸腔中下部有另一对肢体。</li> <li>[数据删除]发觉了正被观察。觉察程度很低，并且目标的物理尺寸限制了任何可能的交流。</li> </ol> <p><strong>姓名：</strong>特工CarrionTrooper<br /> <strong>日期：</strong>10/07/2009<br /> <strong>时间：</strong>约09:10<br /> <strong>时长：</strong>约50分钟<br /> <strong>所见：</strong>迅猛龙群正在猎杀一只似棘龙。他们使用黑曜石刀切肉并把剩下的肉放进他们携带的袋状容器中。屠宰完毕后他们离开了视线范围。就在他们离开后一会，种类未知的小型恐龙快速奔向残骸并且吃掉一些剩下的肉。</p> <p><strong>姓名：</strong>特工Hunter，手持一个摄像机<br /> <strong>日期：</strong>05/17/2009<br /> <strong>时间：</strong>约17:10<br /> <strong>时长：</strong>约45分钟。<br /> <strong>所见：</strong>[特工]首先看到一个孩子骑在一只晃晃悠悠的马上飞来飞去，似乎被“一小群没有敌意的鸟”追逐着。鸟类不属于任何本地品种。他们飞走后，看到了一些树落下，但是没有听到相应的声音。最后，一群像“微型大象”那么大的矮种马走过。<br /> [摄像机]摄像机没有录下任何内容。确切地说，摄像机摄录的内容是一副静止的图像（包括至少两只正在飞的鸟）和普通的森林中的声音。</p> <p><strong>姓名：</strong>Dr.Light<br /> <strong>日期：</strong>08/10/2009<br /> <strong>时间：</strong>8:30<br /> <strong>时长：</strong>约60分钟。<br /> <strong>所见：</strong>一个形状和大小不断变化的微生物，从附近的水体中出现并且在接下来一个小时中重现了人类进化的过程。一开始是一个早期两栖动物，随后慢慢长出后肢，前肢，毛皮，牙齿，开始使用双足直立行走，并且使用木棍作为工具。微生物达到了人类现阶段水平之后又继续进化了约5分钟（手指脚趾变得更长，眼睛变大，身材变小），直到它突然被像是“一只巨大而迅猛的SCP-682”的东西吃掉。Dr.Light提到尽管稍微有些令人困扰，这个过程“带有迷人的科学价值，我真希望我能把它录下来。”</p> <p><strong>姓名：</strong>Dr.Garcia<br /> <strong>日期：</strong>11/11/2010<br /> <strong>时间：</strong>14:45<br /> <strong>时长：</strong>约25分钟。<br /> <strong>所见：</strong>一个充满水（根据████████████████████推测水中含有液态甲烷）的环境，明显处于海拔远低于观察位置的深处。无论是“海面”还是“海底”都不可见，并且光线条件极差。一群会发出生物光的鳐状生物一起从观察点前游过，每只体长都超过40米。</p> <p><strong>Name:</strong> Agent Poe<br /> <strong>Date:</strong> 03/20/2012<br /> <strong>Time:</strong> 17:40<br /> <strong>Duration:</strong> 15 minutes approx.<br /> <strong>Observed:</strong> A huge and oddly distorted human face that emerged from just above the viewpoint. It stared directly at the agent for several minutes before [DATA EXPUNGED]. A number of human-like creatures were seen to form out of the remains, all of which seemed to be aware of their observer.</p> <p><strong>Name:</strong> Dr. Chesnokov<br /> <strong>Date:</strong> 05/15/2012<br /> <strong>Time:</strong> 12:12<br /> <strong>Duration:</strong> 38 minutes approx.<br /> <strong>Observed</strong>: A single male Pan troglodytes (common chimpanzee) appeared from the south-west, into the view of the observation point, carrying the following:</p> <ul> <li>█████ █████-brand smoothie cup, in left hand, with a violet liquid visible through transparent straw.</li> <li>Nondescript smart phone, in its mouth.</li> <li>Novel, entitled █████████, under its right arm.</li> </ul> <p>Chimpanzee made its way to a tree and proceeded to climb upward until it reached a branch eye-level with observer and approximately 30 meters away, before sitting. For the rest of the event, the chimpanzee stared intently at the pages within the book, occasionally sipping from its smoothie and checking its smartphone. This continued for 37 minutes until he suddenly stood and climbed back down, leaving from where he entered.</p> <p><strong>Name:</strong> Researcher Charon<br /> <strong>Date:</strong> 06/05/2012<br /> <strong>Time:</strong> 11:32<br /> <strong>Duration:</strong> 23 minutes approx.<br /> <strong>Observed:</strong> A group of five Suricata suricatta (meerkat), riding an assortment of four wheeled vehicles, similar to &quot;quad-runners&quot;. All were wearing leather vests, on the backs of which were embroidered a large sun in the middle with a halo on top, the words &quot;Sun Angels&quot; surrounding. Coordinating via unintelligible chirrups and barks, they seemed to be searching for something. After about 10 minutes, they formed a large circle, dismounted their vehicles, and began moving inward. When the circle was about 25 meters in diameter, something sprang from the under brush at about the center, and tried to escape. After turning around and seeing that it was surrounded, it tried to make a last stand. The central figure looked like a wolf hominid. The five clan members closed in and eviscerated the wolf creature using their long claws, claiming victory when one of the clan held the wolf's head aloft.<br /> A visibly shaken Researcher Charon noted: &quot;I'm never going to be able to watch The Lion King after <em>THAT!</em>&quot;</p> <p><strong>Name:</strong> Dr. Zara<br /> <strong>Date:</strong> 04/10/2012<br /> <strong>Time:</strong> 11:17<br /> <strong>Duration:</strong> 45 minutes approx.<br /> <strong>Observed:</strong> Plant life unchanged. Fauna not visible, except for a single, enormous horse slowly trekking to the west. Atmospheric dimming suggests horse to be at least twenty kilometers away and more than five kilometers in height.</p> <p><strong>Name:</strong> Researcher Ford<br /> <strong>Date:</strong> 12/10/2012<br /> <strong>Time:</strong> 13:13<br /> <strong>Duration:</strong> 10 min approx.<br /> <strong>Observed:</strong> Researcher Ford looked thoroughly confused upon exiting the tree house. He then explained that he had seen four men in lumberjack attire gathered around a log. None of the men had any apparent facial features. One carried a trumpet that appeared to be made of brass, and was holding it next to where a mouth would be. Another was dribbling a basketball between both his hands. The third carried a birdcage containing a gray bird similar to a pigeon. The last had a jar of peanut butter and a plastic knife that it was using to butter the log. Researcher Ford was oddly concerned with the fact that the peanut butter jar didn't seem to run out even after ten minutes of spreading it on the log. This was noted as within normal parameters and did not warrant any psychological testing.</p> <p><strong>Name:</strong> Dr. Gums<br /> <strong>Date:</strong> 5/27/2013<br /> <strong>Time:</strong> 14:35<br /> <strong>Duration:</strong> 42 min approx.<br /> <strong>Observed:</strong> A swarm of insects resembling Vespa mandarinia (Asian Giant Hornet) were observed to be feeding on the burnt corpse of an unidentified mammal. After about 10 minutes, a live version of the mammal, seemingly on fire and led by what appeared to be a bipedal Crocodylus porosus (Saltwater Crocodile), appeared in-view. The bipedal crocodile proceeded to tear off a low-hanging branch of a nearby tree and carve it into a crude approximation of a flute. About 20 minutes in, it played the makeshift flute, causing the hornets to spasm uncontrollably for a period of about 5 seconds and cease motion. The mammal proceed to systematically crush and consume the hornets for the duration of the observation.</p> <p><strong>Name:</strong> Dr. King<br /> <strong>Date:</strong> 1/17/2015<br /> <strong>Time:</strong> 12:15<br /> <strong>Duration:</strong> Exactly 5 min<br /> <strong>Observed:</strong> Dr. King came out exactly five minutes after having entered, swearing profusely. Eventually, he calmed down enough to explain what he saw. As soon as the vision began, the forest immediately filled with apple seeds up to just below the tree house. It was at that point that he decided he was done testing it.</p> <p>by <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/m-element" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=2941964&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1487494360" alt="M Element" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=2941964)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/m-element" >M Element</a></span></p> 
